Supported Problems (./inputs_files/):

----------------------------------

inputs_bubble_2d
inputs_bubble_3d

A deterministic diffusing bubble with gravity enclosed by walls.  Two of the walls move with
prescribed velocity, creating lid-driven cavity flow.

----------------------------------
The following inputs files were used to generate results in A. Donev et al.,
"Low Mach number fluctuating hydrodynamics of multispecies liquid mixtures",
Phys. Fluids, 27, 037103 (2015)
----------------------------------

