----------------------------------

inputs_paper_thermodiffusion_2d
inputs_paper_barodiffusion_2d

Sec III-C-3. Thermodiffusion and barodiffusion density profiles and structure factors.

----------------------------------

inputs_paper_mmi_3d
inputs_paper_mmi_spectra_3d

Sec IV-B. Mixed-mode instability for heavy saltwater on top of light sugar water.
Comparison to experiments along with analysis of spectra.

----------------------------------

inputs_paper_dlc_spectra_3d

Sec IV-C. Diffusive layer convection instability for light saltwater on top of heavy
sugar water.  Analysis of spectra.

